  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK185">
<l>aṟañcollu neñcattā ṉaṉmai puṟañcollum</l>
<l>puṇmaiyāṟ kāṇap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The emptiness of that man's mind who (merely) praises virtue will be seen from the meanness of reviling another behind his back.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
